**Summary of ASX Announcement (HE8):**  

- **Convertible Note Conversion:** 426,325 convertible notes converted into **85,265,000 new ordinary shares** (ASX: HE8) on 20 June 2025.  
- **Regulatory Disclosure Exemption:** Shares issued without disclosure under Part 6D.2 of the Corporations Act (Section 708A(5)).  
- **Compliance Confirmed:** Company confirms adherence to continuous disclosure (ASX Listing Rules) and financial reporting obligations.  

**No other material information identified.**
